http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#lab.@value: 18-year-old Dani has been trained by her mother to steal things. But they have never stayed in one location long enough for Dani to have connections, real friends, and a real life. In the town of Heaven, everything changes for Dani. Suddenly she must question where her loyalties lie: with the life she's always known, or the one she's always wanted.
